| Synteny witness | POC validated | `verity/witness/synteny.py` |
| Multi-evidence integration | POC validated | `scripts/evaluate_concordance_improvement.py` |

### Key Validation Results

**Latest (December 14, 2025)**:
- Hi-C only discrimination: 0.054
- Hi-C + Synteny discrimination: 0.100 (**+100% improvement**)
- Tested on 3 VGP species: bird (bCalAnn1), mammal, fish
- Speed: 53-363 seconds per assembly (vs 2-4 weeks manual)

Results stored in:
